{"tid":402014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Face Id 係第一部應用Vcsel既手機?","createTime":"2017-09-16T05:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T05:53:01.000Z","uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"79987864da2aa5d70a65190c5376ce7b9ee80adb","tid":402014,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=383&amp;t=5263122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobile01.com%2Ftopicdetail.php%3Ff%3D383%26t%3D5263122&d=3BF22%2F6e999DHfzGWHsj%2Fv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a696ed8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=383&amp;t=5263122</a><br />\n之前睇左台仔呢篇文,有講到iphone X最新技制faceid 以VCSEL放左係手機上面係革新,果邊D ifanboy又係有咁大吹咁大<br />\n<br />\n其實google已經默默地改變左世界而且走得更前,MR/AR android手機已經有2部推左出市場但係無乜人知,因為唔係應用係旗艦機度所以好少人認識<br />\n<br />\n呢個咁有革命性既計畫叫project tango,由google為首開發:<br />\n<a href=\"https://get.google.com/tango/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fget.google.com%2Ftango%2F&d=3BF22%2F6e999DHfzGWHsj%2Fv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=44d30e5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://get.google.com/tango/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wtvox.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/project-tango-sensors.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwtvox.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2Fproject-tango-sensors.jpg&h=017d6f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMS都有類似既技術應用係kinect 2, 可以係PC/Xbox 界面做MR測量,SDK開放左好多年,幫MS開發果間公司叫prime sense,後來apple就收購左幫佢整faceid<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://robohub.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/PrimeSense.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frobohub.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F11%2FPrimeSense.jpg&h=dfd88af5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁MR除左FaceID同Animoji,仲可以有咩應用呢?<br />\n<br />\n1. 立體地圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/project-tango-google-designboom04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designboom.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F02%2Fproject-tango-google-designboom04.jpg&h=0ec6d6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 實景強化<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pprT5GIFxiI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpprT5GIFxiI&d=3BF22%2F6e999DHfzGWHsj%2Fv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6637ea20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pprT5GIFxiI</a><br />\n呢條片有新加坡科學館配合project tango做博物館展示既應用<br />\n<br />\n3. 手機變間尺<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.androidbeat.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/project-tango-main.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.androidbeat.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F02%2Fproject-tango-main.png&h=945a3576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為MR系統可以測量空間物理大小,所以好自然可以拎來當間尺/角尺用<br />\n<br />\n4. 手術導航系統<br />\n可以對人面做定位,再同事先plan左頭部影像register,就可以進行精確既手術導航<br />\n<br />\n5. 泊車<br />\ngoogle auto做野,呢樣唔多講了<br />\n<br />\n點解android唔用呢個技術做face unlock呢?因為google有另一樣更強既face unlock 技術: convolution neural network, source code都放曬上網任人睇任人學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Qualeams/Android-Face-Recognition-with-Deep-Learning-Test-Framework/blob/master/USER%20MANUAL.md\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FQualeams%2FAndroid-Face-Recognition-with-Deep-Learning-Test-Framework%2Fblob%2Fmaster%2FUSER%2520MANUAL.md&d=3BF22%2F6e999DHfzGWHsj%2Fv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=611c051f\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Qualeams/Android-Face-Recognition-with-Deep-Learning-Test-Framework/blob/master/USER%20MANUAL.md</a><br />\n<br />\n點解shamesung會用呢個技術用得咁柒,用一張相都破解到?其實google同facebook一早有真人假人detect,我都唔明點解shamesung有code抄都抄得咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先"}]}